name: Stiicks (25" White)
description:
"Stiicks", from Well Made, are 4 thin strips of American hardwood embedded with several super-strong neodymium rare-earth magnets that sandwich what you're hanging firmly in between. The top pieces mount to the wall, while the bottom weigh down whatever you are hanging. Swapping artwork with Stiicks is simple. Just lift the magnetic slat and put whatever you want in your artwork's place before dropping the Stiick back on top – the magnets will automatically align the frame. For more information please visit our blog post

• print not included
• Rollover the image above for installation example
• Fits 24" wide prints
